\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Good afternoon, everybody.\'a0 Earlier today, I was briefed by my homeland security team on the events in Boston. We\'92re continuing to monitor and respond to the situation as it unfolds.\'a0 And I\'92ve directed the full resources of the federal government
\b\fs18 \cf4 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
